Hollow butterfly
Program to print a hollow butterfly pattern.
Input:- First line will contain an integer n representing the size of the butterfly.
Output-Print a hollow butterfly pattern of size n using.
python code for that-
n=int(input())
for i in range(1,n+1):
    for j in range(1,2*n+1):
        if j==1 or j==2*n  or i==j or j==2*n-i+1:
            print("* ",end="")
        else:
            print("  ",end="")
    print()


for i in range(n-1,0,-1):
    for j in range(1,2*n+1):
        if j==1 or j==2*n  or i==j or j==2*n-i+1:
            print("* ",end="")
        else:
            print("  ",end="")
    print()
